1) Caricare con bash il file ...sh
  1 #! /bin/bash
  2 module load clang/11.0.0
  3 module load cuda/10.0
2) Modificare dentro utilities/common.mk la linea CC=clang
3) Usare -- make CFLAGS="-fopenmp -fopenmp-targets=nvptx64-nvidia-cuda -DEXTRALARGE_DATASET -DPOLYBENCH_TIME" clean a    ll run -- per compilare
